history.content:
Hi friends I need a quick suggestion regarding course enrollments. I am currently waitlisted for 2 classes: I am the 74th on 186's waitlist and 266 on 188's waitlist, while 186 has 0 open seats left and 188 has a bit more than 200.

I am thinking about dropping the one that I am less likely to get in in exchange for another course, but both seem equally likely (or unlikely) and BerkeleyTime doesn't have similar trends. Any advice would be appreciated!
history.subject: Need suggestion for course enrollments.
